  m_Text: 'This platform has a ''RepeatingChangePosition''  receiver attached to
    it. This means that it will cycle between pre-set positions upon receiving a
    positive or negative signal.


    Nearby is an object with the IButton script
    and an IPositiveTransmitter script attached. If the player faces the button object
    and uses interact (F) the platform will move to a designated position. '
